{
  "id": "RAW_2eb4cfe3",
  "title": "两个月前的预测成真：千问 APP 真的打通了阿里生态",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&mid=2247487906&idx=1&sn=ca416365f92d7680b8f9b29878c93059",
  "date": "2026-01-15 03:08:00",
  "author": "花叔",
  "siteName": "花叔",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=be51ff45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxicb2cYotoU8uajOlNDCxw02j8um1Vw3DF0FHk7bzOWuqNyNxoO9ib5kg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #fff !important;padding: 16px 12px 40px 12px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月11日，Google放了个大新闻。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3638888888888889\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004247\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5416d2f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxyp2aap2fUrqR6iaUyCZUA1mc3VdHQWCLOIsWvhmryefUHIm6f17q9Zw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini和沃尔玛达成深度合作——以后你在Gemini里问\"冬天滑雪需要买什么装备\"，AI不只会给你建议，还会直接推荐沃尔玛的商品，甚至可以在对话界面里直接用Google Pay付款。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">沃尔玛的新任CEO说了句很有野心的话：「从传统的搜索到Agent主导的购物，这是零售业的下一次伟大进化。」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">听起来确实厉害。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这件事，千问APP已经低调做了几个月，并且已经快人一步做成了!</span></strong></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近两周，AI圈发生了什么</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实最近两周，AI圈密集发生了好几件事，都指向同一个方向。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月11日，Google宣布和沃尔玛合作搞AI购物。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月12日，Anthropic发布了Claude Cowork。面向普通用户的AI助手，能帮你整理下载文件夹、把收据截图转成费用表格、从桌面笔记生成初稿——简单说就是\"不用写代码的Claude Code\"，帮你处理工作上的事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月15日，阿里的千问App更快一步，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">成功接入淘宝、闪购、高德、飞猪、支付宝，AI购物、AI办事都在千问APP上实现了。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">你发现规律了吗？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Cowork帮你处理工作上的事——整理文件、生成文档、分析数据。而千问，在此基础上，甚至还能帮你处理</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生活上的事</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——点外卖、打车、查政务、买机票。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI正在从\"聊天机器人\"变成\"真正能帮你干活的助手\"。这是2026年AI应用最明显的趋势。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个转变，行业里有个专门的词叫Agent。简单说就是AI不再只是回答问题，而是能主动帮你执行任务、调用工具、完成一整套流程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">问题是，说起来容易，做起来难。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">让AI真正「能办事」，各家有各家的解法</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">让AI帮我们做事，是现在明确的趋势。但怎么做到，不同厂商有不同的思路。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如豆包手机走的是GUI Agent路线，让AI像真人一样操作手机屏幕，帮你点外卖、发微信。这是一种很有想象力的尝试。还有一些厂商在做语音助手的升级，或者通过MCP协议让AI调用各种工具。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里走的是另一条路：</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于自己的生态，从内部打通</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">说到这里，我想起两个月前我写千问的那篇文章。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2OTA1OTAxNA==&amp;mid=2247487271&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=468a9aea9609e8bf7bb912cbc9757cc8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"横扫硅谷的千问，杀回国内了\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">横扫硅谷的千问，杀回国内了</a></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当时千问App刚上线，我在文章最后写了这么一段：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding: 14px 20px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.6 !important;border-radius: 4px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">阿里的商业场景丰富：淘宝、天猫、钉钉、高德、夸克。大胆设想千问有机会可以打通这些产品，真正成为\"AI助理\"。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">想象一下：你在钉钉开会，千问自动生成会议纪要。你在淘宝购物，千问帮你分析哪个商品性价比最高。你在高德导航，千问提醒你路上有什么好吃的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些场景，ChatGPT做不到。因为它只是一个产品，千问背后是一个生态。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个月后，这些场景真的开始实现了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">1月15日，千问App开始灰度测试\"办公助理\"功能，接入了闪购、淘宝、高德、飞猪、支付宝。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5074074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004251\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=069aada4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxv04NibHicnVUayyC3EbJoEEVs6TNCwsaB69ckFHscmpPoWzGSc1hbulQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">打开这个功能，你会看到几个分类：咨询调研（帮你搜集整理全网信息）、office办公（处理表格、生成图表、做幻灯片）、应用开发，以及我们这次重点体验的——</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生活办事</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">生活办事里能做的事还挺多：AI电话预订餐厅、闪购下单咖啡奶茶、跨店闪购美食饮品、智能分析低价机票方案……</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，你也不一定要从这个入口进去。在千问的普通对话框里直接说需求，它也能理解并帮你办事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之所以看好千问这条路，是因为它同时具备两个条件：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，Qwen是SOTA级别的模型。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Qwen系列模型曾在多个榜单上位居全球前三，和GPT、Claude同一梯队。模型能力是做Agent的基础，模型不行，调用再多服务也白搭。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，阿里有丰富的生态可以打通。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;淘宝、闪购、高德、飞猪、支付宝，全是自家产品。API级打通，稳定可靠，支付闭环也能在端内完成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两个条件同时具备的，放眼国内外都不多。OpenAI模型强，但没有生态；很多厂商有生态，但模型差一截。千问可能是少数两者兼备的。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实测：用千问点一杯星巴克</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">说了这么多，还是得实际体验一下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">正好前两天拿到了千问的内测邀请码，趁周末把几个核心功能都试了一遍。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">晚上加班，想点杯咖啡提神。我在千问的对话框里输入：「帮我给家里点一杯星巴克冰美式，我晚上要加班了」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问的反应很快。它先调用淘宝闪购，自动获取了我之前用过的收货地址，然后开始搜索附近的星巴克门店。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1685185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004249\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ed829be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJx36GMkDa9MNgv7QayBuKnO6rdR3QUiaS20TudLBOvYJDhLl6tKmrNW1Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">几秒钟后，千问给我推荐了一款星巴克美式咖啡，显示价格、门店距离、预计送达时间。如果这款不满意，可以左右滑动切换其他选项；地址也随时可以改。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004250\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2027698e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJx5boXaWuy7WaibCT7y7QevCm3ibN7WGSz1iaI9eEf8XGgExbCPiaoh0d8LA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我觉得OK，点了「选它」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后就是让我惊喜的部分了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问不仅帮我完成了下单，还</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动帮我匹配了最大优惠</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，省了14块。整个订单从30块变成24.5块。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1685185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004248\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa4e80d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJx4XeoyMMUPj3NY9lYb5J08LGf0q0LdCTicjaLDwglH7p3l9wBMHtV6EA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，付款这一步还是需要我自己确认——毕竟涉及到钱，AI自动扣款还是有点吓人的。但支付宝的密码输入界面直接在千问App内弹出，输完密码就完成了，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">全程不用跳转任何其他App</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004256\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=18bc131b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxt57bEg0RFTnPnwrQwmXOOiazP1uiaicSP5jLm4miaGtjN6Km7ZqpIecmfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程，从输入需求到付款完成，大概1分钟。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前点个外卖，得打开外卖软件，搜索店铺，选商品，填地址，找优惠券，确认支付。现在一句话，千问全帮你搞定了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种丝滑感，是我之前用其他AI助手没体验过的。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实测：用千问订机票</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">既然能点咖啡，订机票应该也不在话下。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次我故意「为难」了一下千问，提了个比较复杂的需求：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">「帮我查一下下周一从上海到北京的机票，要10点以后出发，不要到大兴机场的，以及尽量便宜些，给我提供不同时段的选择」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">说实话，这个需求如果让我自己在携程或飞猪上筛选，得花好几分钟反复设置筛选条件。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问的反应让我有点惊喜。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004255\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=790a52e5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxnQJlAH1nye7oASyxwjsyzEAZY4UY6kUtantAzfGuUPZztI4FZYrzKQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">它不仅理解了我的所有约束条件，还主动做了分析：「目前符合'首都机场+低价'的航班主要集中在傍晚至晚上时段」，「若坚持要在上午10点后出发且落地首都机场，目前低价区间的航班选择极少」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后给我整理了</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三个梯度方案</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：下午出发的、晚间出发的、以及价格最优的。每个方案都列出了航班信息、推荐理由、亮点。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004254\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06832f2e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxgGgZSQeRaRjhApAcLdqzE3URlcAzrNobHckQEsxVxMFiaPeDeZjj9hg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种「帮你分析+给你选项」的模式，比单纯列一堆航班信息有用多了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">我选了方案一，点击「订票」，直接在千问App内进入了飞猪的预订页面。更丝滑的是，</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我之前在飞猪留存过的个人资料都自动带过来了</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，不用重新填写乘机人信息。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1675925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004253\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13ec176a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxa9EiaTMrOyFeIjgMcyBVVPc4l6B23vibAGaJNUp713xgzG8Za8ibQbReA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种跨服务的数据打通，才是阿里生态的真正优势。换成其他AI助手，就算能帮你搜到航班，你还是得跳转到第三方App重新登录、重新填信息。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">意外之喜：政务服务</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了购物和出行，千问还接入了一个让我意外的场景：政务服务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次更新，千问还深度接入支付宝的政务服务，支持50项民生服务的查询和办理。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这解决了一个真实的痛点。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前想办一件事——比如给新生儿办医保、查公积金、办护照——你得先搜索大量信息，搞清楚归哪个部门管、需要什么材料、去哪个网站办理。不同城市的政策还不一样，经常查半天也搞不清楚。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在呢？直接问千问：「杭州户口怎么办护照」或者「如何给新生儿办理医保」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">千问会告诉你：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding-left: 28px;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">能不能办</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">需要准备什么材料</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 12px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">直达办理入口</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个功能背后是千问和支付宝政务服务的打通。支付宝本身就接入了大量政府服务，现在千问可以直接调用这些能力，用自然语言帮你理清办事流程。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">50项民生服务，签证、户口、公积金、社保迁移，都能查。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 24px;font-weight: 600;color: #fff !important;line-height: 1.4 !important;margin: 40px 0 24px;padding: 16px 24px;background-color: #d32f2f !important;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这不是终点，是起点</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个月前我写千问的文章，最后一段是这么说的：</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 24px 0;padding: 14px 20px;border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.6 !important;border-radius: 4px;background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">中国的ChatGPT，不是梦想，而是现实。这不是终点，是起点。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1435185185185186\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 600px !important;height: auto;display: block;margin: 32px auto;border-radius: 6px;border: 2px solid #d32f2f;box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.12);\" data-imgfileid=\"100004252\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e95c707f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FHRdaeEmxNHYSXkmpuVXlN8At6XLoXRJxxstjI3qWgokDUtiahiaNcWmicJlCpnAzyQiayCGKcQ2R3ibn9ic1h8U2rdpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在看，千问确实在兑现这一预言。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google和沃尔玛的合作才刚宣布，千问已经能帮我点咖啡、订机票、查政务了。这不是因为国内技术领先多少，而是因为阿里有独特的生态优势——</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">自家的服务自己打通，不需要跟别人谈判</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI助手的竞争，最终比的不是谁更会聊天，而是谁能真正帮你办事。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">而现在，阿里“最强模型”与“最丰富生态”的结合，正在将全球AI竞赛带入新阶段。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，目前千问的\"办公助理\"功能还在邀请测试阶段，体验上肯定还有优化空间。但方向是对的：AI不应该只是一个问答机器，它应该成为你生活中真正能帮上忙的助手。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.9 !important;color: #1a1a1a !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">点咖啡、订机票、查政务，这些听起来都是小事。但</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 700;color: #d32f2f !important;background-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">小事办得顺，才是真正的\"能办事\"</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文揭示了阿里云千问 APP 如何先于 Google 与沃尔玛的合作，打通淘宝、高德、飞猪、支付宝等阿里生态服务，实现了 AI 购物、出行与政务办理等 Agent 功能，展示了“最强模型”与“最丰富生态”结合的独特优势。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文揭示了阿里云千问 APP 如何先于 Google 与沃尔玛的合作，打通淘宝、高德、飞猪、支付宝等阿里生态服务，实现了 AI 购物、出行与政务办理等 Agent 功能，展示了“最强模型”与“最丰富生态”结合的独特优势。",
  "summary": "文章分析了当前 AI 应用从“聊天机器人”向“Agent（助手）”转变的趋势，指出 Google 与沃尔玛合作的 AI 购物模式虽具野心，但阿里的千问 APP 已先行一步，低调实现了阿里生态内部的打通。文章详细阐述了千问 APP 接入淘宝、闪购、高德、飞猪、支付宝，实现 AI 购物、AI 办事的功能，包括智能点餐、机票预订、甚至政务服务查询办理。作者认为，千问的成功在于其兼具 SOTA 级模型能力和阿里丰富的内部生态，这种“模型+生态”的组合优势是其他厂商难以复制的。通过实测点咖啡和订机票的流畅体验，以及意外接入政务服务的惊喜，文章强调了千问真正“能办事”的价值，并预言其将全球 AI 竞赛推向一个新阶段。",
